                <h1>How to Find Windows 10 Lock Screen Wallpaper Location</h1>
                <p>Windows 10 lock screen wallpapers are typically stored in the `C:\Windows\Web\Screen` directory. This folder contains the default images used by the lock screen. If you've set a custom wallpaper, it may be found in your Pictures library or the location you specified during the wallpaper selection process.</p>
